TRACCIA:
Modellizzare la struttura di una tabella per
memorizzare tutti i dati riguardanti delle auto usate 
messe in vendita da un concessionario

nome repo: db-first
autore: Simone Di Meglio
______________________________________________________

name: cars

Column                  Type                    Attributes                          Index

id                      BIGINT UNSIGNED         AUTO_INCREMENT, NOT NULL, UNIQUE    PRIMARY KEY
automaker               VARCHAR(150)            NOT NULL                            INDEX
model                   VARCHAR(150)            NOT NULL                            INDEX
generation              VARCHAR(100)            NULL
vin                     VARCHAR(17)             NOT NULL, UNIQUE
class                   VARCHAR(100)            NOT NULL
launch_year             YEAR                    NOT NULL
fuel_type               VARCHAR(100)            NOT NULL                            INDEX
engine_type             VARCHAR(150)            NULL
engine_displacement     VARCHAR(50)             NOT NULL
engine_horsepower       VARCHAR(50)             NOT NULL
gearbox                 VARCHAR(50)             NOT NULL 
length                  FLOAT(6,2)              NOT NULL
weigth                  FLOAT(6,2)              NOT NULL
height                  FLOAT(6,2)              NOT NULL
doors                   TINYINT                 NOT NULL 
previous_owners         TINYINT                 NULL
description             TEXT                    NULL
picture                 VARCHAR(255)            NULL
price                   FLOAT(7,2)              NOT NULL                            INDEX



legenda/description of column keys 

id                      unique id of cars
automaker               name of automaker brand (ex Ford, Tesla, Jeep, Dodge etc.)
model                   name of the model (ex Raptor, Model T, Wrangler, Nitro etc.)
generation              (ex 2nd gen etc.)
vin                     chassis number (unique alphanumeric code)
class                   type of vehicle (ex suv, sedan, minivan, station-wagon etc.)
launch_year             when the car was launched on the market
fuel_type               type of power supply (ex gas, petrol, diesel etc.)
engine_type             name of engine (ex Euro 6d Final etc.)           
engine_displacement     engine displacement (italian = cilindrata - ex 2000cm^3)
engine_horsepower       engine horsepower (italian = cavalli motore - ex 300cv)
gearbox                 gearbox type (ex manual, automatic etc.) 
length                  car's length
weigth                  car's weigth
height                  car's height
doors                   numbers of doors
previous_owners         numbers of possible previous owners
description             description of cars (accessories, problems, characteristics, the condition in which it is found)
picture                 main picture
price                   selling price
